Common.Highlight.Common.Text: In the heart of busy North Sydney CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive listing agent is pleased to present Shop 4, 83 Mount Street, North Sydney. A secure investment opportunity situated in the heart of North Sydney’s bustling business precinct. Having been a popular Japanese restaurant for over 10 years, the property has become a local institution with a loyal customer base. The tenant, Taruhachi Bento, is extremely highly rated with 4.7 stars out of 5 on Google from over 250 reviews cementing it as one of the best and most popular restaurants in North Sydney. The lease has just been extended by the tenant to 31 August 2026 with options to 2036. With 4% fixed annual reviews, a bank guarantee and guarantor the lease ticks all the boxes of the most discerning investors. Further to this, North Sydney is undergoing a phase of unprecedented growth with commercial and residential development which will only strengthen the customer base. 

Shop 4, 83 Mount Street, North Sydney benefits from the following key attributes:

•Net annual Income of $57,098* secured by a Bank Guarantee and Guarantor
•Lease to 31 August 2026 with options to 2036
•Valuable fixed 4% annual rental increases
•Highly rated and established Japanese Restaurant tenant
•Situated in the heart of the bustling North Sydney central business precinct
•Unprecedented growth with commercial and residential development in the area, strengthening the tenant's customer base



For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approx.
